card_text: Activate 1 of these effects, also, after that, Set this card face-down instead of sending it to the GY.$N●Change 1 Set "Subterror" monster on the field to face-up Attack or Defense Position.$N●Change 1 face-up "Subterror" monster on the field to face-down Defense Position.$N●ATK/DEF of 1 "Subterror" monster on the field become equal to its combined original ATK/DEF until the end of this turn.$N●This turn, activated effects of "Subterror" cards cannot be negated.
